   - Fixed 3 bps per leg for now
   - Can upgrade to model later

**Result:** Should drop APY by ~10-15 pp (57% â†’ 42-47%)

### Phase 2: Add Execution Reality (3 days)

**Operational penalties:**
4. âœ… **Partial fills** (90% execution)
5. âœ… **Missed hedges** (10% doesn't earn funding)
6. âœ… **Ops skip** (0.5% daily skip probability)

**Result:** Should drop APY by additional ~3-5 pp (42-47% â†’ 37-44%)

### Phase 3: Add Safety Buffers (2 days)

**Conservative hurdles:**
7. âœ… **Tighter hurdle** (4 bps instead of 3 bps)
8. âœ… **Wider no-trade bands** (10% instead of 5%)
9. âœ… **Borrow unavailability** (5% daily probability)

