## ðŸ’¡ Key Philosophy

**"Backtest harder than reality":**

- If V1.5 (harsh) shows **35-40% APY** â†’ Live will likely exceed **40-45%**
- If V1.5 (harsh) shows **< 30% APY** â†’ Don't deploy (too marginal)
- If V1.5 (harsh) shows **> 45% APY** â†’ Amazing, deploy aggressively

**Safety margin:** 5-10 pp between harsh backtest and live expectations.

